Lokhu kuvele empendulweni yoMqondisi jikelele woMnyango weMfundo ePhakeme uMnuz Gwebs Qonde, obephendula uSolwazi Belinda Bozzoli ePhalamende, okhulumela iDA emfundweni ePhakeme. USolwazi Bozzoli ubuze ukuthi zingaki izitshudeni ezishiya phakathi izifundo zingaqedile ukufunda. Impendulo yomnyango ithe zingu-122 769 ezishiya phakathi zingaqedanga ukufunda. “Kulezo ezingu-31 627 kuneminyaka emithathu zishiyile, ezingu-67 348 zineminyaka emithathu kuya phezulu zishiyile kanti ezingu-23 794 akukadingeki ukuthi zibuyise imali. I-NSFAS ayisibuzi isikhungo ukuthi kungani isitshudeni sishiye phakathi ukufunda singaqedanga,” kuphendula uQonde. Izitshudeni ezishiye phakathi yilezo ezingaphothulanga ukufunda zibe zixhaswe isikhwama futhi zingafundi. UQonde uthe iNSFAS iyakwazi ukubona izitshudeni eziphothule izifundo zazo. Uthe isikweletu sikhokhwa uma isitshudeni sesisebenza sesihola ngaphezulu kukaR30 000 ngonyaka. Abakweletayo kumele baxhumane nabesikhwama babazise ukuthi sebeyasebenza ukuze bakhokhe. I-NSFAS isebenzisana nabaqoqa izikweletu abazimele ukuze baxhumane nabakweletayo ukuze kuqoqwe imali. Kuthunyelwa nezitatimende ukuze abakweletayo bazi ukuthi sebekweleta malini kanti lesi sikhwama sisebenzisana nophiko oluqoqa intela kuleli iSars ukuthola abakweletayo. UQonde ephendula umbuzo kaNksz Hlomela Bucwa weDA obebuza ukuthi yimalini ebikweletwa yizitshudeni ngonyaka wezimali * -2016/2017, uthe nguR2.543 billion.